precision mediump float; uniform mat4 mg_TextureMatrix; uniform sampler2D mg_Texture0, mg_Texture1; uniform vec4 mg_Color; uniform float mg_Texture0_Weight, mg_Texture1_Weight, mg_Color_Weight; uniform vec4 mg_Texture0_Modulate, mg_Texture1_Modulate; uniform bool mg_Transparent_Title_Enabled; uniform vec2 mg_Transparent_Title; uniform float mg_Transparent_Title_E; varying vec2 mg_UV0, mg_UV1; vec2 transform_uv(vec2 uv) { vec4 v = vec4(uv, 0, 1); v = mg_TextureMatrix * v; return v.xy; } void main() { vec4 col = vec4(0, 0, 0, 0); if(mg_Transparent_Title_Enabled && gl_FragCoord.y >= mg_Transparent_Title[1]) { discard; } if(mg_Texture0_Weight > 0.05) { col += mg_Texture0_Modulate * texture2D(mg_Texture0, transform_uv(mg_UV0)) * mg_Texture0_Weight; } if(mg_Texture1_Weight > 0.05) { col += mg_Texture1_Modulate * texture2D(mg_Texture1, transform_uv(mg_UV1)) * mg_Texture1_Weight; } if(mg_Color_Weight > 0.05) { col += mg_Color * mg_Color_Weight; } if(mg_Transparent_Title_Enabled && gl_FragCoord.y >= mg_Transparent_Title[0]) { col = clamp(col, vec4(0), vec4(1)); float total = mg_Transparent_Title[1] - mg_Transparent_Title[0]; float toTop = mg_Transparent_Title[1] - gl_FragCoord.y; float scale = toTop / total; col.a *= pow(scale, mg_Transparent_Title_E); } if(col.a < 0.01) { discard; } gl_FragColor = col; }

uniform mat4 mg_ModelView, mg_Projection; attribute vec2 mg_TexCoord0, mg_TexCoord1; attribute vec3 mg_Vertex; varying vec2 mg_UV0, mg_UV1; void main() { gl_Position = mg_Projection * mg_ModelView * vec4(mg_Vertex, 1); mg_UV0 = mg_TexCoord0; mg_UV1 = mg_TexCoord1; }
